  "Description": {
    "English": "A map of a nearby planet. A <span class=\"name name-special\">a relic of an ancient civilization</span> has been marked.<br><br>Select the map and use <VAL_ON>Plot Route (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>)<> to pin the location in your Exosuit display.<br><br>New maps can be gained by exchanging <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Navigation Data</span> with a Space Station Cartographer.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一张附近行星的地图，标有一个<span class=\"name name-special\">古代文明的遗物</span>。<br><br>选择地图并使用<VAL_ON>规划路线（<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>）<>以在你的套装屏幕中标记该地点。<br><br>新地图可以通过与空间站制图师交换<span class=\"name name-commodity\">导航数据</span>获取。",
    "TencentChinese": "一张附近行星的地图，标有一个<span class=\"name name-special\">古代遗物地点</span>。<br><br>选择地图并使用规划航线（<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>）以在你的套装屏幕中固定该地点。<br><br>新地图可以通过与空间站制图师交换<span class=\"name name-commodity\">导航数据</span>获取。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "附近行星的地圖，已標記一處<span class=\"name name-special\">古老文明遺物地點</span>。<br><br>選取地圖後，使用<VAL_ON>規劃路線功能 (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>)<> 即可在你的強化套裝顯示器中釘選該地點。<br><br>與太空站地圖學家交換<span class=\"name name-commodity\">導航資料</span>，即可獲得新星系圖。"
  },
